# Our Privacy Policy
This page is used to inform Users regarding our policies.
We DO NOT collect, store or use any personal or non-personal information while you visit, download or upgrade our mobile apps.
Our applications use or may use advertisng currently provided by following services and anonymous statistical information is reported to them so they can see whether their adverts are effective such as Device Or Other IDs (ex : Advertising ID). Click each ad service provider to see more information about their privacy policy.

- Facebook Audience Network
- Admob Ads
- Chartboost

We currently dont use any analytic solution, maybe we will use it in the future to better understand how our users interact with the app and to catch errors.
